persons: Sheik Butti bin Suhail Al Maktoum
subject: Soccer
lead_paragraph: The Royal Emirates Group of Companies, a Dubai business group headed by Sheik Butti bin Suhail Al Maktoum, bought the Spanish club Getafe.
